window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Book 8 of the hit Defiance of the Fall LitRPG series is now available!</b></p> <p><b>About the series</b>: Jump into a story that merges Apocalyptic LitRPG elements with eastern cultivation. Class systems, skill systems, endless choices for progression, it has everything fans of the genre love. Explore a vast universe full of mystery, adventure, danger and even aliens, where even a random passerby might hold the power of a god. Follow Zac as he struggles to stake out a unique path to power as a mortal in a world full of cultivators.</p>"; 
